    Enum Constants
    Enum Constant
    Description
    CRAFTING
    The output is actively being crafted.
    ERROR
    A generic job error state.
    FINISHED
    All expected outputs are crafted.
    INVALID
    If this job, or its dependencies, have missing storage instances.
    INVALID_INPUTS
    The recipe inputs could not be inserted into the crafting handler.
    PENDING_DEPENDENCIES
    The crafting job has been scheduled, but is not processing yet because a dependency is still being processed.
    PENDING_INPUTS
    The crafting job has been scheduled, but is not processing yet because input ingredients are missing.
    QUEUEING
    The crafting job has been scheduled, but is not processing yet because other jobs are still processing.
    UNSTARTED
    No outputs have been crafted yet, and they are not scheduled yet for crafting.
